{"tid":2031453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通過香港人權法時又話中共嚇到瀨屎， 而家通過國安法又話香港政府嚇到瀨屎 ！","createTime":"2020-05-23T11:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T12:05:28.000Z","uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"910973cbb693aa3dd983dceb5dfcea5d0881bfe8","tid":2031453,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"事實係連登時事台鍵盤戰士嚇到瀨屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b39faf2a5485cae3e1c0962cd67bac147745b3e","tid":2031453,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">524 港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span>"},{"pid":"3b9bc626bc89756dd6a463f48466b9a21848d67f","tid":2031453,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}